text: 60Beans is so blessed with friendly neighbours, supportive Locals & community members, best of all, our enthusiastic & energetic baristas and staff. You guys are wonderful!
This is my new favorite cafe. It will wake up my soul, love it so much. coffee lover have to try.
Stumbled into this cafe on a recent trip to Toronto. Great coffee at this new and yet-to-be-discovered cafe. Quality espresso without a crazy line, which is hard to find these days.
